                <div align="center">
                  <center>
                  <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse: collapse" bordercolor="#111111" width="93%" id="AutoNumber1">
                    <tr>
                      <td width="100%">
                      <p align="justify" style="word-spacing: 1; line-height: 200%; margin-top: 11; margin-bottom: 18">&nbsp;&nbsp;
                      <font face="Times New Roman">
                      <font color="#452E14" style="font-size: 15pt">&nbsp; The 
                      XXIX General Assembly of the International Union of Radio&nbsp;&nbsp; 
                      Science (Union Radio Scientifique Internationale-URSI) 
                      will be held at&nbsp;&nbsp; the Hyatt Regency Chicago 
                      Hotel in downtown Chicago, Illinois, USA on&nbsp; August 
                      07-16, 2008. The General Assemblies of URSI are held at&nbsp;&nbsp; 
                      intervals of three years to review current research 
                      trends, present new&nbsp;&nbsp; discoveries and make plans 
                      for future research and special projects in all&nbsp;&nbsp; 
                      areas of radio science, especially where international 
                      cooperation is&nbsp;&nbsp; desirable. The first Assembly 
                      was held in Brussels, Belgium in 1922 and&nbsp;&nbsp; the 
                      latest in New Delhi, India in 2005. Assemblies were held 
                      in the USA&nbsp;&nbsp; on three previous occasions: in 
                      Washington, D.C. in 1927 and 1981, and&nbsp;&nbsp; in 
                      Boulder, Colorado in 1957.<br>
                      <br>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; We look forward to seeing you in Chicago in 
                      2008.</font><b><font style="font-size: 15pt"><br>
                      &nbsp;</font></b></font></p>
                      <p align="center" style="word-spacing: 1; line-height: 200%; margin-top: 11; margin-bottom: 18">
                      <b>
                      <font face="Times New Roman" color="#D4BDA8" size="1">
                      webmaster: oguzhan akgol</font></b></p>
                      <p align="justify"></td>
